{
  "stem": "23498.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went with his brother-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then-- he-- he had two brothers, with two brothers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because the youngest brother wife was from Brest, which was close to the Russian frontier, she went too with her children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was only a few days, and he couldn't be separated from his family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He knew that he's the strong one and he will-- in-- in a sort of a danger, he will help us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he came back, leaving behind the middle brother and the younger brother with his family, and we never heard about them anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The middle brother, the Max, came back after some time to-- decided to come back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But before he-- he came back, it was still the bombardment was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were-- you see, they were partnered to all the business, and they had a beautiful apartment in [INAUDIBLE] which was a main street in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a center, and it was opposite the station, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that brother Max asked my father to go to Warsaw to look after his family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was really silly of us to go there because the bombardment was mostly in the center, you see, and especially on that main station, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Central station.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father being so-- such a family man, and he loved all his family, we went there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And luckily we survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was about months or so, the-- the war, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you were there until?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came in, and I saw them marching, and it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were thousand of people on both side of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first came the-- the Germans on the motorcycles and then the others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were watching.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
